text: America's Next Top Model, Cycle 18 "British Invasion" is the eighteenth cycle of ANTM. This cycle includes British models from Britain's Next Top Model (BNTM) who didn't win. The winner was 22-year old Sophie Sumner from Oxford, England. The cycle had a total of 14 contestants, 7 seven American and 7 British. ==Prizes== * A modeling contract with LA Models & NY Model Management * A spread in Vogue Italia * A $100,000 contract with
